cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on Japanese predicate argument structure analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also employs neural networks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses multi-task learning, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.CY (Computational Geometry).
